STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Andrew J. FEDE, Defendant-Petitioner. C-608 September Term 2017
079997 Supreme Court of New Jersey. March 12, 2018 To the Appellate Division, Superior Court: A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001296-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same; It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is granted; and it is further ORDERED that Michael A. Orozco, Esquire, is assigned to represent defendant on the appeal before this Court; and it is further

ORDERED that assigned counsel for defendant may file and serve a supplemental brief on or before April 27, 2018, the State may file and serve a supplemental brief in response on or before May 29, 2018, and defendant may file and serve a supplemental reply brief on or before June 13, 2018.
